{"tid":1242261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解李家超條廢物可以做到呢個位?","createTime":"2019-06-19T03:46:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T15:41:10.000Z","uid":132931,"like":745,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":127,"replies":[{"pid":"02daa139a8baffd2ac60ed5ab1733dd151783560","tid":1242261,"uid":132931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:46:55.000Z","msg":"睇緊立法會會議,發現李家超真係廢到無倫不特止,仲有種目中無人feel.<br />\n一係跟稿讀一係遊花園,之前逃犯條例D會議已經覺得佢鴻鳩嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c361323bc27bf018f10ef7e9309987a3baf712","tid":1242261,"uid":132931,"like":19,"dislike":4,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:48:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇緊立法會會議,發現李家超真係廢到無倫不特止,仲有種目中無人feel.<br />\n一係跟稿讀一係遊花園,之前逃犯條例D會議已經覺得佢<span style=\"color: red;\">濕</span>鳩嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"77c61db8bf0e66453145c62e821ba763f2625c02","tid":1242261,"uid":12633,"like":439,"dislike":1,"score":438,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:48:23.000Z","msg":"成個政府都係咁，成埋廢物高薪厚祿"},{"pid":"42daaec6e1aef72cbe893a80ff86eb2a6d0c47eb","tid":1242261,"uid":81569,"like":0,"dislike":56,"score":-56,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:50:15.000Z","msg":"其實比卡超定聰sir實權大啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42aed2c1665b5a39d69c007d78c4b9c6e9e87dc8","tid":1242261,"uid":257422,"like":50,"dislike":2,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:50:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">阻一阻你個post, 有d提議：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n除左要傾行動細節<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我覺得星期五 既 主題 應該要集中加強 於</span> <br />\n<br />\n追究警察濫權濫用武力 ！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先講建議：</span><br />\n1. 將依項命題提高到 同反送中 一樣高度/重要性！<br />\n2. 老土d, 黎緊日子整多d 中英示威大Banner關於警察濫權、濫用暴力、同醫館局私通 既問題，追究責任！<br />\n3. 議員都應該要有共識去追究依個問題<br />\n4. 加強各種文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原因：</span><br />\n<br />\n關於行動主題，我地要識得運用火種<br />\n將香港人團怒火keep住燒：<br />\n<br />\n無錯，撤回係未達成，但人人都知個問題，團火已經係白熱化，所以口號照叫，但唔好只集中於依個命題；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，明日大嶼/雙普選/國歌法都係係大問題，但現實就係依幾個議題好難吸引到大多數市民，太新、太遠，我地可以將佢地加插入我地既討論，但好難成為民意大爆發既火種，只可以乘住其他議題去帶出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反地，警察醫館局資料互通、差佬亂打青年人,和平示威者,女示威者、監警會無呀老虎，依d都係實實在在最令市民嬲既議題，亦都係國際社會既人權關注重點，我地一定要將依個命題加強到同反送中一樣高度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daad4b706297e566bdf4251a04c373f66561520f","tid":1242261,"uid":29093,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:51:15.000Z","msg":"未死就排到佢 <br />\n<br />\n政府， 公營機構見唔少啦"},{"pid":"01a438f214f44b65ddc36183d329b933c5ffd05f","tid":1242261,"uid":181778,"like":70,"dislike":1,"score":69,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:51:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fdab00724f1c8c4b98ab49afaf82738aee4ef617","tid":1242261,"uid":2419,"like":135,"dislike":2,"score":133,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:52:27.000Z","msg":"廢係必要條件黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6a117a1ad5bc42986011f1a7c1e509d0b5c3250","